.
 Then there exists a neighborhood 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\epsilon}\left(c\right)\in A$
\end_inset

.
 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

 be chosen such that 
\begin_inset Formula $c+h,c-h\in V_{\epsilon}\left(c\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Thus we can take the limit
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{h\to0}\frac{g\left(c+h\right)-g\left(c-h\right)}{2h},
\]

